Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:06.32,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:06.32,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:12.69,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:12.69,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:27.37,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:27.37,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:39.12,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:39.12,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:44.62,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:44.62,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:50.13,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:50.13,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:56.40,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:56.40,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:01.71,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:01.71,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:07.41,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:07.41,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.18,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.18,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:35.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The cicadas and the crickets are crying together...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:37.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At ten o'clock at night, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this summer or fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:42.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:45.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do cicadas usually cry this late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:48.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up, summer's over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:50.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get to go anywhere yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:53.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is supposed to be the last\Nsummer break of my student days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:01:59.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost been a month, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:00.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:03.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Hagu-chan went back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan's home is in Nagano, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:10.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what she'll bring us back...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:13.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll probably bring back some nozawana...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:14.86,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,50)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Nozawana: {\be1\3c&H000000&}prickled turnip leaves, soba: buckwheat noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:14.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe some soba...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:22.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Area code 0263?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:24.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:24.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:26.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:29.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:30.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:32.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just on our way back from the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:33.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:34.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:35.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:36.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:38.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's sweet and sour at the same time, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:39.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:41.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:42.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:44.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we want?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:51.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Shuu-chan-sensei is asking whether\Nyou want some nozawana or some soba.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:55.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, she wants to know whether we\Nwant some nozawana or some soba.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:56.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They want meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:00.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then soba it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:05.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants us to come have soba for dinner,\Nsince they're coming back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Soba?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...she's coming back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.76,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard her voice over the phone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:24.72,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,If feels like my ears keep tingling...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:28.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:29.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:33.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that ring tone just now, Mayama-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:35.81,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it from a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.61,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, it's "Moon River."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san, that melody just now—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:46.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto, I'm sorry, but take these back for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:49.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:53.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's up with Mayama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:57.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Mayama-san had a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:00.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san, do you know who she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:05.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:09.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,About tonight's soba party...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:14.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Morita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:18.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd try to cut down on my electricity bill...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:21.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't mean you should use someone else's electricity...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:23.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You even brought your console...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:26.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think people would normally do this to each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:31.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you'll die if you sleep with the\Nair conditioner and the fan running.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll freeze to death, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, such warm air.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:38.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you catch a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make it to tonight's soba party?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:42.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:47.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see her face, since it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:55.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if I don't take new pictures, I can't update my site...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, that Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:01.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san doesn't seem to be back either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:04.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do about the soba party...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:07.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:08.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:12.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We've just received an urgent request.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:14.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Care to help us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:19.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a soba party to go to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:21.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The deadline is the day after tomorrow, 19:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:24.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're willing to pay you in cash if you make the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be glad to accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You caught a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:38.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The 246 seems to be backed up due to construction...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:41.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, I guess I'll just have to take the Komazawa pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:50.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:52.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should get some sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:54.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be pretty rough until the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So... it's just you, Takemoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:03.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:05.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They all went somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's completely okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:09.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll just split the treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...between the three of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:15.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That smells so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:22.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cow's tongue is best when grilled over charcoal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...with the windows open and the fans on max.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:26.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:27.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I tell you about vegetables and meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:29.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratio two to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:31.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Eat your veggies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:38.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Hagu-chan seem really close, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've been looking after her since she was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:45.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I attended her field days in place of her dad, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:50.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you could say that I half raised her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:53.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...or should I say that she's like a daughter to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:56.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so this is your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:56.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not listening at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:02.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The walls are all covered with books.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan loves books.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:09.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are these chairs stuck together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:10.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where I sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:13.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these dolls with dreadlocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:18.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Jenny-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:21.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy and Shuu-chan bought them for me when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:23.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I made the clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:24.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty skillful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:28.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did you make this design...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:29.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:30.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to make one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:32.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.40,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got long eyelashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:42.65,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,They're casting a shadow on her cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:46.70,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm really having fun right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:51.04,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one thing for a grown-up man to be playing dolls with a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:57.04,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I think about how she can make such splendid\Nclay statues that even men can't make...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:03.38,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It amazes me that she makes such small\Ndoll clothes with those same hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:08.09,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she is quite feminine, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:09.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:11.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A Neolithic woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:17.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a piece of cloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:19.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A Paleolithic woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:22.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I take back what I just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:23.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The finished ones are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:27.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:28.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A wardrobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:29.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A wardrobe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it just a tissue box?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:38.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it be that you're just not very good with tools?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:44.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to make you a wardrobe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:46.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am an architecture major...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:51.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I guess I'm quite used to making models...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:53.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:56.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe one of those with the sliding doors?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:58.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.06,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)\pos(428,102)\c&H3D3B34&\3c&H3D3B34&\bord3\be1\shad1.4\fscx60\fsp18\b0\fs70\fnArtificeSSK\1a&HFF&\4c&H3E3831&\frz1.29}Rococo World
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:01.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rococo style?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:05.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How long does Takemoto intend to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:07.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, he still hasn't gone home yet, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:13.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But then again, they're pretty quiet now, even though\Nthey were a bit noisy until a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:16.83,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't have!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:22.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna slice you up, Takemoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rococo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:36.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have doubted you for even a fleeting moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:39.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Versailles...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:40.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:43.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As a sign of my apology...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll pay for the materials at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:49.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Versailles...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:01.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The sun's so bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:02.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:06.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well, like I was saying, one of our assignments\Nduring high school for summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:05.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I even trying so hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...was on Natsume Souseki's "Kokoro"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:10.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rococo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:15.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:17.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:19.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:22.73,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H679BC8&\fs34\bord1\shad2\be1\4c&H1F3052&}tora (tiger){\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&} + uma (horse) = torauma (trauma)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:21.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rococo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:24.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get the successive Rococo attacks of the Hanamoto family...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:24.23,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H679BC8&\fs34\bord1\shad2\be1\4c&H1F3052&}tora (tiger){\c&HF8DAA8&} {\c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H383838&}+ {\c&H3A526B&\4c&H16292B&}uma (horse){\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&} = torauma (trauma)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:27.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...out of my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:27.69,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H679BC8&\fs34\bord1\shad2\be1\4c&H1F3052&}tora (tiger){\c&HF8DAA8&} {\c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H383838&}+ {\c&H3A526B&\4c&H16292B&}uma (horse) {\c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H383838&}= {\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H635514&3c&H000000&}torauma (trauma)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:25.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rococo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:31.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:32.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:36.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting then. Call me if you need anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:39.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If I end up borrowing the chair...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:41.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back here in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:44.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you then since I'll need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:46.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:48.80,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:51.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:53.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With an older woman this time, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.47,0:10:58.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She even gave him a lift to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:11:00.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have spent the night out. What a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:03.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:06.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san, that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:10.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:12.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:15.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't broken up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and end it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:18.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:24.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, how many more girls will\Nhave to cry for you to be satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:51.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yamada! Yamada! Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:29.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:30.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:34.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't care less about you sowing your wild oats on sterile land...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:40.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But stop showing up to socials and taking girls back\Nhome like they're take-out delivery, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:42.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:47.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of mine from another school has been\Nflooding me with questions about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:48.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:51.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:55.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you taking a picture for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:59.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally bought my 4.32 megapixel camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:02.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now, what are you taking a picture of?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:06.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:07.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Taro doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:10.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Back when Yamada-san was a freshman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:16.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She ran the six kilometers to school every morning\Nin order to help her dog Taro on its diet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:20.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and has earned the nickname "Iron Lady" from her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:20.81,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&H2F3E5A&\fad(500,0)\bord0.6\shad0\frz15\3c&H363E5C&\pos(57,56)}Named
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:17.76,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H274392&\fs24\frz2\shad0\bord0.5\fscx80\pos(182,46)\3c&H4157A1&}Iron Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.76,0:12:17.80,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H274392&\fs35\frz2\shad0\bord0.5\fscx80\pos(177,44)\3c&H4157A1&}Iron Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:17.84,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H274392&\fs45\bord1\fscx80\frz2\shad0\pos(187,48)\3c&H4157A1&}Iron Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.81,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\bord1.1\fscx80\frz2\shad0\pos(187,49)\c&H2C4BA5&\3c&H2C4BA5&}Iron Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:20.89,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&H2F3E5A&\bord0.6\shad0\frz17\3c&H363E5C&\pos(504,60)}Named
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:21.01,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&H2F3E5A&\bord0.6\shad0\frz17\pos(620,60)\3c&H363E5C&}Named
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:20.89,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\bord1.1\fscx80\frz2\shad0\c&H2C4BA5&\3c&H2C4BA5&\pos(634,51)}Iron Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:21.01,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\b1\bord1.1\fscx80\frz2\shad0\c&H2C4BA5&\3c&H2C4BA5&\pos(751,51)}Iron Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:22.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't change the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:25.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be more respectful when talking to your senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:27.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same grade level!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:30.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When did my girl become so hateful?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:33.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama doesn't remember raising you this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:35.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:39.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san's... Morita-san's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, he got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:47.25,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp6\fscx70\frz-20\1a&H64&\shad0\bord0\b0\fs50\pos(228,360)\c&H757B7E&\frx344\fry322}Infirmary
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:53.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Morita-san's going to be okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:57.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A crutch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:01.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:05.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But why is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:10.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry for calling so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:14.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's completely okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:17.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:18.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:23.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How's work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your body holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:28.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Setting my health aside, it's really inconvenient...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:31.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...to only be able to use my right arm standing\Nup, especially when I'm so busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:34.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even take notes by myself. It's really annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:36.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's probably no use telling you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:43.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:47.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm getting along really great since Mayama-kun's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:49.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he being helpful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, very much so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:51.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:56.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was getting worried about it, since I was the\None who introduced him to you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:59.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It goes without saying that he's very dedicated to his work...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.53,0:14:01.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's also quick-witted and pretty clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:05.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's only 22, but he's rather sneaky...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:09.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and deals with people well, so he's a big help to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:11.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you praising him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:12.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:17.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the type you can rely on when working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:21.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:26.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So what was it again? You say you\Nneed a chair for your photo shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:28.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Two, three days should be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:33.69,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who that person was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:36.15,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed pretty close to Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:40.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking at, Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:45.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of eating these with Shuu-chan-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:51.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he can eat those right now\Nbecause he has a guest over, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:52.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:58.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, are you famished by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:01.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:02.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:02.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:06.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mika was really great right then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:08.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,First she drew eyebrows on the dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:08.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:10.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On a Shiba dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:12.39,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:15.56,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen Hagu-chan hang out\Nwith friends or anything, have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:20.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I walked all around town like that, I was dog-tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, why don't we go to Shimokita today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:25.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a shop I want to visit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:28.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, Asami's ex-boyfriend showed up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:31.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why all CDs cost 3,000 yen a piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:32.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm broke here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:34.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:35.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want some sweet chestnuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This Caramel Macchiato really is something, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:40.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:43.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think my... stomach hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:45.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:47.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:48.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:58.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll feel better soon, so lie down a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:04.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, she left this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:05.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:08.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be fine once she rests.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:13.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:19.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, who was that woman here just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Rika?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:24.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really beautiful, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:28.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let her know you said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:31.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she Mayama-san's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:38.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, Morita-san said Mayama-san had a girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:41.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And Mayama-san left and didn't come back after some phone call...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:46.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then this morning he came to school in a taxi with her, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:50.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Their relationship isn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:53.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:55.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:16:58.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've bought you the materials and tools\Nyou need to build Hagu's wardrobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:00.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I got everything that came to my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:04.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A semicircle saw, a pen-shaped router...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:06.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A 45 degree cutting board and other miscellaneous materials!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:09.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I also have this really effective glue...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:12.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rococo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:24.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always run away when the going gets tough?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:29.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you keep following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:33.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you keep running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:35.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to just keep running away like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:38.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:41.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just going to keep working at her office?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:45.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you just tell her that you like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:52.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just going to go with the flow\Nlike that without saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:54.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:57.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:00.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you blow steam at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:02.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:06.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're better off finding another guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:11.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:15.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:17.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:21.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:29.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:32.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:36.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've packed the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:38.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:40.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I come with you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:42.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:44.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's the chair, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:48.19,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}boku no kotoba ga tarinai no nara
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:48.19,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If my words are not enough for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:47.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call the staff members who are on location. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:51.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry that I held you back for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:57.95,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}mune wo naifu de saite eguridashite mo ii
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:57.95,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can rip my chest open and cut out the heart with a knife
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:54.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you really helped me out, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:57.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you again. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:07.38,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kimi no mayoi to iiwake gurai
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:07.38,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even I have noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:17.47,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}honto wa boku datte kizuiteta no sa
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:17.47,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your excuses and hesitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:17.47,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I never told him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:21.02,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,But he already knew how I felt about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:29.69,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}itsuka mata anna fuu ni dareka wo nikumu no ka na
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:29.69,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Will I someday hate someone like that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:25.23,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if she also can't answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:28.15,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,While already knowing his feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:34.78,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,His love may not come true as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:35.24,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}datoshitara motto motto
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:35.24,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If so, then I will more and more embrace you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:39.87,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,And my tears just won't stop flowing when I think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:44.21,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}dakishimete toge no you ni kokoro ni sasareba ii
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:44.21,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And you can pierce my heart like a splinter,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:54.22,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}anata ni zutto zutto nokoreba ii
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:54.22,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just as long as I can remain forever in your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:50.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:53.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better take in some fluid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:56.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll shrivel up if you lose too much water.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:07.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:11.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's all smiles to other people because\Nhe wants to show them his good side...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:16.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But when he can't hide his flaws, he\Nalways gets scared and runs away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:21.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He even gave up on that woman thinking that\Nhe can't make her come to him by himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:25.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't do anything because he's afraid that he'll look bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:28.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:29.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A big idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:33.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:38.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you like him so much if you know that he's such an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:40.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:42.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:44.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always liked him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:50.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I like him, but I can only think of his bad side...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:53.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet I think I want to hear his voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:57.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And hold hands with him, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:02.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:03.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:07.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in love, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:08.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:12.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so calmly observing me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:14.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why after all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:15.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's love!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:16.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:28.02,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}akanai mabuta kosutte mieru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:28.02,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I rub my heavy eyelids to reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:33.15,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}pastel moyou no mirai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:33.15,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}A future in the shape of pastels
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:40.28,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}chiribamerareta kigou o tadoru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:40.28,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I follow the scattered symbols
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:44.37,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}taguri yoseta hyoujou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:44.37,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}As my expressions were pulled in closer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:50.12,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}nee nandakke sagashiteita mono
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:50.12,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Say, what was it that we were looking for again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:53.21,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}are wa soune itsudakke
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.67,0:21:53.21,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}That's right, exactly when were those days
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.17,0:22:00.59,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}bokura ga inryoku ni sakarai nagara deatta koro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.17,0:22:00.59,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}When we used to meet, denying the attraction\Nthat was forming between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:06.52,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sore ga waltz no you dane fushigi sa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:06.52,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}It's like a waltz, isn't it? It's quite marveling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:12.73,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sasayaku youna komorebi no kousaten de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:12.73,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}We paint away sceneries
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:18.95,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}futari waltz no youni ne mawari nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:18.95,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}As we waltz and spin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:25.08,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}egaki dashite yuku mono
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:25.08,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}Where the whispering sunlight falls through the trees and meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.83,0:22:33.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: He and she sway.
